rows.label: tlk45350251_01_msg0001
rows.name:
In Superbia, research on Divine
Beasts and weaponry is a common
pursuit even at private institutions.

rows.label: tlk45350251_01_msg0002
rows.name:
It's subsidized by the
government, you see.

rows.label: tlk45350251_01_msg0003
rows.name:
For our current project here, we're
researching ways to encourage plant
life to grow on this Divine Beast.

rows.label: tlk45350251_01_msg0004
rows.name:
If we could grow our own vegetables,
we'd be less dependent on imports,
and it might help to recover too.

rows.label: tlk45350251_01_msg0005
rows.name:
That's the dream, anyway.
All we can do right now
is experiment and hope!
